# The effects of the added potions are as follows:
![effect list](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f68c7d01104bbd61e88ab796eec605a1f225f977.png) 
# Mod Overview  
This mod adds rich new status effects and related enchantments to Minecraft, expands potion brewing mechanics, and supports full custom configuration.  
# Potion Effects  
### Positive Effects  
1. 生命静止（Static Life）: All damage and healing effects are delayed until the effect ends;  
1. 坚盾（Solid Shield）: Reduces damage from other entities by level;  
1. 限伤（Injury Limitation）: Caps incoming damage at a percentage of maximum health (scales with level);  
1. 不死（Immortal）: Grants one revival per level upon fatal damage, restoring health and consuming one effect level;  
1. 免疫（Immune）: Grants resistance to negative effects per level; Level V negates all negative effects;  
1. 吸血（Leeching）: Restores a percentage of health based on damage dealt;  
1. 近战领域（Melee Domain）: Expands an immunity zone around the player by level (configurable);  
1. 长距（More Range）: Increases attack range per level;  
1. 触及（Touch）: Increases mining reach per level;  
1. 真伤（True Damage）: Converts a portion of damage to armor-ignoring true damage per level;  
1. 自愈（Self-Healing）: Restores a percentage of current health based on level and health percentage;  
1. 飞行（Flight）: Grants flight; speed increases with level;  
1. 修复（Repair）: Periodically repairs equipped gear durability by level;  
1. 流血抵抗（Bleeding Immunity）: Counters or shortens bleeding effects; resists leeching;  
1. 精准（Accurate）: Boosts ranged damage by a percentage per level;  
1. 巨力（Huge Force）: Increases melee damage by a percentage per level;  
1. 百分比恢复（Percentage Recovery）: Periodically restores a portion of maximum health by level;  
1. 高踏（Step Up）: Increases automatic step height per level;  
1. 坚定（Firm）: Boosts armor, armor toughness, and knockback resistance per level;  
1. 闪避（Evasion）: Increases dodge chance per level (configurable);  
1. 生命链接（Injury Link）: Reflects damage to nearby entities when injured;  
1. 屠戮（Slaughter）: Deals increased damage to targets with lower remaining health;  
1. 盛宴（Feast）: Rapidly heals when hunger is high; consumes health to replenish hunger when low;  
1. 同伴（Companion）: Boosts attributes and restores health when nearby same-type entities die (limited uses);  
1. 位格（Rank）: Strengthens attributes against non-players and inflicts debuffs based on rank difference; grants buffs against players (spawn rules configurable);  
1. 适应性（Adaptation）: Extends post-damage invulnerability duration per level;  
1. 庇护（Asylum）: Periodically grants Absorption Hearts; accumulates refresh time when hearts are full;  
1. 过量治疗（Overdose Treatment）: Converts excess healing into Absorption Hearts (capped);  
1. 魔力聚焦（Magic Focus）: Increases magic damage by a percentage per level;  
1. 魔法护盾（Magic Shield）: Reduces magic damage by a percentage per level;  
1. 强心（Strong Heart）: Amplifies healing effects by a percentage per level;  
1. 回响打击（Resonant Strike）: Triggers a secondary attack of the same damage type on hit;  
1. 不屈意志（Unyielding Willpower）: Grants a chance to survive fatal damage and gain Absorption Hearts;  
1. 速攻（Fast Attack）: Reduces the target’s invulnerability ticks per level;  
1. 延时（Extension）: Mode 1: Extends duration of newly applied effects; Mode 2: Prevents duration decay for specific effects per level (configurable);  
1. 亡命之债（Life Debt）: Deals retaliation damage to the killer and inflicts a curse upon death;  
1. 踏空（Airstride）: Generates invisible blocks beneath the player;  
1. 效果窃取（Effect Siphon）: Steals a potion effect from the target on hit (max level = current effect level - 1);  
1. 复用（Reuse）: Stores active buffs as throwable potion bottles;  
1. 随机正面效果（Random Positive Effect）: Grants a random positive effect;  
1. 匿踪（Veiled Presence）: Causes all entities to ignore the player unless attacked;  
1. 渊博（Erudite）: Multiplies experience drops by effect level on kill;  
1. 暴食（Gluttony）: Accelerates eating and drinking speed;  
1. 升级（Upgrade）: Randomly upgrades lower-level effects when gaining new ones;  
1. 挖掘强化（Enhanced Digging）: Boosts mining speed and mining level simultaneously;  
1. 爆燃（Deflagration）: Deals (remaining burn time (ticks)/20) * level fire damage per tick; ends with explosion dealing remaining time (ticks) * level fire damage;  
1. 反弹（Recoil）: Reflects the same damage type back to the attacker;  
1. 快速拉弓（Quick Draw）: Increases bow-drawing speed. 
2. 范围攻击 (Attack AOE): Deals area-of-effect damage based on effect level and a specific percentage on attack;
3. 攀爬 ((Climbing)): Grants spider-like wall-climbing ability for the duration;
4. 镇静 (Calming): Prevents screen shaking when damaged and grants immunity to Fear effects of equal or lower level;
5. 穿透 (Pierce): Allows fired arrows to pierce through additional entities based on the effect level;
6. 生命转化 (Health Conversion): Restores health equal to (Damage * 20% * Level) after taking non-armor-piercing damage;
7. 追踪 (Homing): Makes fired regular arrows track the nearest target;
8. 动能 (Kinetic): Adds damage based on the player’s current movement speed when attacking; 

### Negative Effects  
1. 护甲破裂（Armor Broken）: Reduces armor value and toughness per level;  
1. 流血（Bleeding）: Inflicts periodic physical damage per level;  
1. 恐惧（Fear）: Cooldowns held items and drastically reduces damage dealt per level;  
1. 溃力（Wane）: Reduces attack damage;  
1. 脆弱（Fragile）: Increases damage taken by a percentage per level;  
1. 窒息（Suffocation）: Drains oxygen per level;  
1. 弱效回复（Weakening Recovery）: Reduces healing effectiveness by a percentage per level; Level V blocks healing entirely;  
1. 腐蚀（Corrosion）: Periodically degrades gear durability per level;  
1. 沉重（Heavy）: Increases gravity and reduces movement speed per level;  
1. 剧毒（Highly Toxic）: Inflicts periodic armor-ignoring toxic damage per level;  
1. 伤势累积（Injury Accumulation）: Deals internal damage based on lost health and level (increases when injured);  
1. 伤势爆发（Injury Outburst）: Explodes internal damage upon effect end (based on lost health and level);  
1. 失准（Misalignment）: Reduces ranged damage by a percentage per level;  
1. 禁锢（Imprison）: Fully restricts movement and jumping;  
1. 病毒（Virus）: Inflicts damage and spreads infection; triggers same-level virus effects when infection maxes;  
1. 诅咒（Curse）: Applies multiple debuffs and prevents duration decay of other negative effects;  
1. 混乱（Confusion）: Causes random teleportation per level;  
1. 衰变（Decay）: Reduces maximum health per second (restored after effect ends);  
1. 破碎魔抗（Broken Magic Shield）: Increases magic damage taken by a percentage per level;  
1. 魔力抑制（Magic Inhibition）: Reduces magic damage dealt by a percentage per level;  
1. 驱散（Dispel）: Lowers the level of all positive effects on the target;  
1. 随机负面效果（Random Negative Effect）: Inflicts a random negative effect.  
2. 众矢之的 (Aggro): Attracts aggro from nearby entities;
3. 死亡 (Death): Deals damage related to effect level and max health when the duration ends. If the entity survives, it receives a higher level of the Death effect;
4. 空间锚定 (Spatial Anchor): Higher levels block more methods of teleportation;
5. 药水拮抗 (Potion Antagonism): Reduces the duration of newly acquired effects to (0.5^Level). If this effect’s level is greater than 3, the level of newly acquired effects is reduced by (Current Level - 2);
6. 副作用 (Side Effect): While active, acquiring a new positive effect also inflicts several negative effects (configurable, disabled by default);
7. 鱼肺 (Gills): Drains oxygen when out of water and restores oxygen when in water.

### Neutral Effects  
1. 燃命（Health Sacrifice）: Loses health per second while boosting damage (scaling with duration and level);  
1. 轻装上阵（Lightly Loaded）: Increases movement speed but reduces armor and damage resistance per level;  
1. 重甲（Heavy Armor）: Decreases movement speed but boosts armor and damage resistance per level;  
1. 赌徒（Gambler）: Randomly doubles damage dealt/taken (multiplier range scales with level and Luck stat);  
1. 燃烧（Combustion）: Sets the target on fire; duration shortens in water;  
1. 借势（Leverage）: Converts movement speed into damage (and recoil damage) per level;  
1. 锁定（Lock）: Prevents effect removal (except by duration decay);  
1. 随机效果（Random Effect）: Grants random effects (positive/negative/neutral; quantity scales with level).  
2. 槽位锁 (Slot Lock): Prevents dropping items while the effect is active.

# Enchantments  
1. 消法之刃（Elimination Effect）: Randomly removes a potion effect on hit;  
1. 惩法之刃（Potion Punisher）: Deals bonus damage to targets with potion effects;  
1. 不屈（Unyielding）: Grants temporary Static Life on fatal damage;  
1. 碎甲之刃（Sunder Armor）: Applies Armor Broken on hit with a chance;  
1. 剧毒之刃（Highly Toxic Blade）: Applies Highly Toxic on hit with a chance;  
1. 腐败施加（Infliction Corrosion）: Applies Corrosion on hit with a chance;  
1. 抑疗（Inhibit Therapy）: Applies Weakening Recovery on hit with a chance;  
1. 生机勃勃（Vibrant）: Grants Strong Heart while worn;  
1. 飞行（Flying）: Grants Flight while worn (loot-only);  
1. 祝福之源（Source of Blessing）: Grants a random positive effect on hit with a chance;  
1. 诅咒之源（Source of Curseing）: Inflicts a random negative effect on hit with a chance.  

# Custom Brewing System  
- Supports adding custom brewing recipes via JSON configuration: 
- Potions can have multiple status effects simultaneously; 
- custom potion names and colors are configurable; 
- auto-generates config folder and sample recipe to `/config/more_potion_effects/example_recipe.json` on first launch; 
- crafted potions auto-added to Creative Mode inventory; compatible with JEI for viewing custom recipes.  

# Commands  
/force_effect or /fe: Force effect management command; supports forcibly adding/removing effects (ignores immunity).  

# Configuration Options  
Provides extensive configuration; 
numerical values adjustable in `more_potion_effects.toml`: Configure random effect exclusion lists; adjust specific effect parameters; set visual behaviors for specific effects.
